%F A002320 Sequences A002310, A002320 and A049685 have this in common: each one satisfies a(n+1) = (a(n)^2+5)/a(n-1) - _Graeme McRae_, Jan 30 2005
%F A002320 G.f.: (1-2x)/(1-5x+x^2). - _Philippe Deléham_, Nov 16 2008
